    FROM \"SubCategoris\" AS \"s\"
    LEFT JOIN \"Objects\" AS \"o\" ON \"s\".\"SubCategoriID\" = \"o\".\"SubCategoriID\"
) AS \"t\" ON \"c\".\"CategoriID\" = \"t\".\"CategoriID\"
